details.sectionContent: An open-source mobile application Software Development Kit created by Google.

We all are familiar with usage of various mobile applications and its importance in our daily life. So we are organizing a workshop on Flutter so that we can develop applications for both Android and IOS devices using one common language and one common platform.
This is a workshop by Parth Jhansaria (GDGâ€™s Flutter Head). Participants are required to come with fully charged laptops and enthusiasm to explore.
